SN,<string> -> Changes name
+ -> echo mode
$$$ -> command mode
--- -> exit command mode
R,1 -> reboot
SH,<value> -> Change HID flag register to value -> value = 0220 for mouse
S~,<value> -> Change prolfile -> 0 for SPP, 6 for HID. reboot is needed 
SF,1 -> reset to factory default
S~,<string> -> Change serialized friendly name of the device
ST,<value> -> 1 <= value <= 252 set command mode timeout to value